<p:sld xmlns:a="http://schemas.openxmlformats.org/drawingml/2006/main" xmlns:r="http://schemas.openxmlformats.org/officeDocument/2006/relationships" xmlns:p="http://schemas.openxmlformats.org/presentationml/2006/main"><p:cSld><p:spTree><p:nvGrpSpPr><p:cNvPr id="1" name=""/><p:cNvGrpSpPr/><p:nvPr/></p:nvGrpSpPr><p:grpSpPr><a:xfrm><a:off x="0" y="0"/><a:ext cx="0" cy="0"/><a:chOff x="0" y="0"/><a:chExt cx="0" cy="0"/></a:xfrm></p:grpSpPr><p:sp><p:nvSpPr><p:cNvPr id="2" name="Rectangle 1"/><p:cNvSpPr/><p:nvPr/></p:nvSpPr><p:spPr><a:xfrm><a:off x="457200" y="304800"/><a:ext cx="8229600" cy="1754326"/></a:xfrm><a:prstGeom prst="rect"><a:avLst/></a:prstGeom></p:spPr><p:txBody><a:bodyPr wrap="square"><a:spAutoFit/></a:bodyPr><a:lstStyle/><a:p><a:pPr algn="just"/><a:r><a:rPr lang="en-US" b="1" dirty="0"/><a:t>3. Documentation Process</a:t></a:r><a:endParaRPr lang="en-US" dirty="0"/></a:p><a:p><a:pPr algn="just"/><a:r><a:rPr lang="en-US" dirty="0"/><a:t>All dispatches are accompanied by complete documentation as per </a:t></a:r><a:r><a:rPr lang="en-US" b="1" dirty="0"/><a:t>CPCB and MPCB</a:t></a:r><a:r><a:rPr lang="en-US" dirty="0"/><a:t> guidelines:</a:t></a:r></a:p><a:p><a:pPr marL="285750" indent="-285750"><a:buFont typeface="Arial" pitchFamily="34" charset="0"/><a:buChar char="•"/></a:pPr><a:r><a:rPr lang="en-US" b="1" dirty="0"/><a:t>Manifest Document</a:t></a:r><a:r><a:rPr lang="en-US" dirty="0"/><a:t>:</a:t></a:r><a:br><a:rPr lang="en-US" dirty="0"/></a:br><a:r><a:rPr lang="en-US" dirty="0"/><a:t>A 5-copy manifest system (as per Hazardous Waste Rules) is used for traceability from source to destination.</a:t></a:r></a:p></p:txBody></p:sp><p:sp><p:nvSpPr><p:cNvPr id="3" name="Rectangle 2"/><p:cNvSpPr/><p:nvPr/></p:nvSpPr><p:spPr><a:xfrm><a:off x="457200" y="2059126"/><a:ext cx="8153400" cy="2585323"/></a:xfrm><a:prstGeom prst="rect"><a:avLst/></a:prstGeom></p:spPr><p:txBody><a:bodyPr wrap="square"><a:spAutoFit/></a:bodyPr><a:lstStyle/><a:p><a:pPr marL="285750" lvl="0" indent="-285750"><a:buFont typeface="Arial" pitchFamily="34" charset="0"/><a:buChar char="•"/></a:pPr><a:r><a:rPr lang="en-US" b="1" dirty="0" smtClean="0"/><a:t>Form10</a:t></a:r><a:r><a:rPr lang="en-US" dirty="0"/><a:t>:</a:t></a:r><a:br><a:rPr lang="en-US" dirty="0"/></a:br><a:r><a:rPr lang="en-US" dirty="0"/><a:t>Issued to the co-processing unit mentioning total weight, batch numbers, and AFR characteristics.</a:t></a:r></a:p><a:p><a:pPr marL="285750" lvl="0" indent="-285750"><a:buFont typeface="Arial" pitchFamily="34" charset="0"/><a:buChar char="•"/></a:pPr><a:r><a:rPr lang="en-US" b="1" dirty="0" smtClean="0"/><a:t>Certificate of </a:t></a:r><a:r><a:rPr lang="en-US" b="1" dirty="0"/><a:t>Analysis (COA)</a:t></a:r><a:r><a:rPr lang="en-US" dirty="0"/><a:t>:</a:t></a:r><a:br><a:rPr lang="en-US" dirty="0"/></a:br><a:r><a:rPr lang="en-US" dirty="0"/><a:t>Provided with each dispatch, detailing the calorific value, moisture content, ash content, and other essential parameters.</a:t></a:r></a:p><a:p><a:pPr marL="285750" lvl="0" indent="-285750"><a:buFont typeface="Arial" pitchFamily="34" charset="0"/><a:buChar char="•"/></a:pPr><a:r><a:rPr lang="en-US" b="1" dirty="0"/><a:t>Transporter Details</a:t></a:r><a:r><a:rPr lang="en-US" dirty="0"/><a:t>:</a:t></a:r><a:br><a:rPr lang="en-US" dirty="0"/></a:br><a:r><a:rPr lang="en-US" dirty="0"/><a:t>Vehicle registration, driver's license, route plan, and emergency contact information are recorded and verified.</a:t></a:r></a:p></p:txBody></p:sp><p:sp><p:nvSpPr><p:cNvPr id="5" name="Rectangle 4"/><p:cNvSpPr/><p:nvPr/></p:nvSpPr><p:spPr><a:xfrm><a:off x="457200" y="4644448"/><a:ext cx="8229600" cy="2031325"/></a:xfrm><a:prstGeom prst="rect"><a:avLst/></a:prstGeom></p:spPr><p:txBody><a:bodyPr wrap="square"><a:spAutoFit/></a:bodyPr><a:lstStyle/><a:p><a:r><a:rPr lang="en-US" b="1" dirty="0"/><a:t>4. Transport and Handover</a:t></a:r><a:endParaRPr lang="en-US" dirty="0"/></a:p><a:p><a:pPr marL="285750" lvl="0" indent="-285750"><a:buFont typeface="Arial" pitchFamily="34" charset="0"/><a:buChar char="•"/></a:pPr><a:r><a:rPr lang="en-US" dirty="0"/><a:t>The loaded jumbo bags are </a:t></a:r><a:r><a:rPr lang="en-US" b="1" dirty="0"/><a:t>securely placed in the transport vehicle</a:t></a:r><a:r><a:rPr lang="en-US" dirty="0"/><a:t>, ensuring stability and safety.</a:t></a:r></a:p><a:p><a:pPr marL="285750" lvl="0" indent="-285750"><a:buFont typeface="Arial" pitchFamily="34" charset="0"/><a:buChar char="•"/></a:pPr><a:r><a:rPr lang="en-US" dirty="0"/><a:t>Vehicles used are compliant with hazardous material transportation norms and are equipped with </a:t></a:r><a:r><a:rPr lang="en-US" b="1" dirty="0"/><a:t>spill kits</a:t></a:r><a:r><a:rPr lang="en-US" dirty="0"/><a:t> and </a:t></a:r><a:r><a:rPr lang="en-US" b="1" dirty="0"/><a:t>fire extinguishers</a:t></a:r><a:r><a:rPr lang="en-US" dirty="0"/><a:t>.</a:t></a:r></a:p><a:p><a:pPr marL="285750" indent="-285750"><a:buFont typeface="Arial" pitchFamily="34" charset="0"/><a:buChar char="•"/></a:pPr><a:r><a:rPr lang="en-US" dirty="0"/><a:t>At the receiving end (cement plant), proper </a:t></a:r><a:r><a:rPr lang="en-US" b="1" dirty="0"/><a:t>handover procedures</a:t></a:r><a:r><a:rPr lang="en-US" dirty="0"/><a:t> are followed, with </a:t></a:r><a:r><a:rPr lang="en-US" b="1" dirty="0"/><a:t>acknowledgment copies</a:t></a:r><a:r><a:rPr lang="en-US" dirty="0"/><a:t> of the manifest collected and archived</a:t></a:r></a:p></p:txBody></p:sp></p:spTree><p:extLst><p:ext uri="{BB962C8B-B14F-4D97-AF65-F5344CB8AC3E}"><p14:creationId xmlns:p14="http://schemas.microsoft.com/office/powerpoint/2010/main" val="1263585730"/></p:ext></p:extLst></p:cSld><p:clrMapOvr><a:masterClrMapping/></p:clrMapOvr><mc:AlternateContent xmlns:mc="http://schemas.openxmlformats.org/markup-compatibility/2006" xmlns:p14="http://schemas.microsoft.com/office/powerpoint/2010/main"><mc:Choice Requires="p14"><p:transition spd="med" p14:dur="700" advClick="0" advTm="1000"><p:fade/></p:transition></mc:Choice><mc:Fallback xmlns=""><p:transition spd="med" advClick="0" advTm="1000"><p:fade/></p:transition></mc:Fallback></mc:AlternateContent><p:timing><p:tnLst><p:par><p:cTn id="1" dur="indefinite" restart="never" nodeType="tmRoot"/></p:par></p:tnLst></p:timing></p:sld>